name: Honey Stinger Vanilla Mini Waffle 150g
description:
The bright sweetness of honey, blended with the subtle smoothness of vanilla, sandwiched between 2 thin waffles and ready to provide a quick hit of carbs on a long ride. Also excellent with coffee or tea as a mid-morning snack.100% organic ingredients.Ingredients: wheat flour, palm fruit oil, brown rice syrup, sugar, eggs, soy flour, sea salt, honey, natural flavour, soy lecithin, rice extract and baking soda.Contains: wheat, soy and eggs.May contain milk.
